aboutMeText1: My name is Luana Barreto, I am a Physiotherapist and currently perform home care in the areas of Elderly health, Trauma-orthopedics and Lymphatic Drainage.
aboutMeText2: I have an immense love for Physiotherapy, because through it I was able to give back the will and the strength to live. To live with quality, through personalized services where each patient is unique.
aboutMeText3: Physiotherapy for me goes far beyond a profession, it is a mission.
